  - **Middle Layer:** A green rectangular block placed horizontally on top of the arch (1 block).

  - The blue cube is centered on the green block.
  - The orange triangular roof block is placed on top of the blue cube.
  - Two orange cylindrical blocks are positioned vertically on either side of the blue cube.
